  "description": "Nestled within a private gated community in one of Marbella’s most sought-after locations, Villa La Alquería offers a perfect balance of modern comfort and Mediterranean charm. This stylish 4-bedroom villa boasts breathtaking views over Alquería Golf Course and the iconic La Concha Mountain, providing a serene and luxurious retreat for families and groups.\n\nStepping inside, the villa welcomes you with bright and spacious interiors, tastefully designed with soft, neutral décor. The open-plan layout flows effortlessly from the dining and living areas to a second TV lounge, creating a relaxed and inviting atmosphere. A fully equipped kitchen, featuring Bosch appliances and a Nespresso coffee machine, leads to a lovely breakfast terrace overlooking the golf course. A separate laundry room adds extra convenience.\n\nThe villa’s split-level design enhances its sense of space, with a mezzanine-style living room opening onto a covered terrace, complete with a comfortable lounge area and stunning views. Just a few steps away, a charcoal BBQ terrace provides the perfect setting for alfresco dining. The villa’s private pool invites guests to cool off while taking in the picturesque scenery.\n\nVilla La Alquería features four beautifully appointed bedrooms. The first, located on the main level, includes a queen-sized bed, an ensuite bathroom, and direct access to the pool terrace. Upstairs, the second and third bedrooms—one double (160cm) and one twin—offer golf course views and share a spacious bathroom with a bathtub and double sinks. The impressive master suite boasts a king-sized bed, a large ensuite with a bathtub and separate shower, a TV, and a private terrace with panoramic views.\n\nAdditional amenities include a gym machine in the basement, individual air conditioning units in every room, wall-mounted radiators for winter comfort, and high-speed WiFi throughout. Guests also have access to a padel court within the secure 24-hour-patrolled community.\n\nPerfectly positioned just minutes from Marbella’s pristine beaches, world-class golf courses, lush parks, and the vibrant Puerto Banús, Villa La Alquería offers an unbeatable location for an unforgettable stay. With its contemporary design, open-plan living, and idyllic surroundings, this villa is the ultimate holiday retreat, blending luxury with the beauty of the Mediterranean lifestyle.",
